  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nIn ssz-v2 branch, Job Wait Time some time jumps to > 2 min\r\n+ A lot of peers get penalized due to broken promises (when it's >3s from the promise time)\r\n+ Mesh peers are 0 or 1, hence gossip blocks are rarely received\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1607\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2022-02-23 at 11 29 18\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/155272297-fd6ca0dd-effe-4c1b-8561-5f696d53f418.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\n+ Job wait time should be consistently <2s in order not to get penalized for broken IWANT promises\r\n+ Job time of Aggregate_AndProof topic should be consistently around 125ms as seen in healthy node\r\n+ There are no gap in the metrics, ie there are always jobs to run\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\n\r\nIt sometimes happen on ssz-v2 branch, sometimes it does not",
